project_descr: SUPPORT TO THE UN COORDINATION FOR RESULTS IN CUBA

outputs.output_descr:
TO STRENGTHEN THE COORDINATION OF UN SYSTEM IN CUBA FOR KEY RESULTS: THE UN SYSTEM IS COMPRISED OF 7 RESIDENT AGENCIES AND 8 NON-RESIDENT AGENCIES.
THE AGENCIES WORK IN COHESION AND COORDINATION FOR THE DELIVERY OF SPECIFIC ACTIVITIES IN KEY RESULT AREAS SUPPORTING NATIONAL PRIORITIES.
